{"tid":1906672,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印尼一對母女感染新型肺炎　是當地首次出現確診病例","createTime":"2020-03-02T05:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T05:52:46.000Z","uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e785695373bdc82e49da0f0acd09fca6ac9d2daa","tid":1906672,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511957-20200302.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511957-20200302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igU2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=ad359cd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511957-20200302.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1fc5e369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511957-20200302.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n印尼首次出現新型肺炎確診病例，衛生部長說，當地有兩人確診，分別是一名64歲女子及她的31歲女兒，兩人對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陽性，目前在雅加達一間醫院留醫，並無出現嚴重呼吸困難症狀。<br />\n<br />\n印尼官員說，一名日本人早前從馬來西亞返回印尼後確診，這對母女同這名日本人可能曾經有密切接觸。<br />\n<br />\n另外，新加坡傳媒報道，當地新增兩宗確診病例，患者都曾到印尼巴淡島，並無到過中國或南韓旅遊。"},{"pid":"49083a023038f073b0581147c2c135421fb3776e","tid":1906672,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:47:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b11d384b0b0f6a936e634b21149e9953f827c0d0","tid":1906672,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"一名日本人早前從馬來西亞返回印尼後確診<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞？定日本？"},{"pid":"7b7435838d2c801c09b590a0fbcfd194cb5c73a7","tid":1906672,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>每日to-DO List</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. Twitter 戰線<br />\n2. 去tvb廣告商fb洗版<br />\n3.幫襯黃色經濟圈</span><br />\n4.壯大黃圈youtuber, Dislike 藍絲Youtuber<br />\n<span st